profile_positions.description:
As senior ERP Implementation Consultant I have been responsible for the implementation of the following ERP/CRM systems:

-Epicor (ERP system)
-Platinum for Windows (PFW)(ERP system)
-Batchmaster/PFW (ERP system specifically for process manufacturing)
-Clientele (CRM application)

In relation to these applications, the following tasks have been performed:
-Project Manager for various implementation projects; 
-Technical Installations and Upgrades;
-Analysis Business Requirements and System Design;
-Definition Customizations: Translation of User Requirements to Technical Specifications;
-Conversion of Historical Data, as well as various Euro conversions;
-Development of Forms and Reports with Crystal Reports;
-Development and maintenance of Training material. Training of end-users;

Examples of customers: Citrix, Inver UK Ltd, Compuware Ltd,  Ben & Jerry’s, Pennzoil,  Ring!Rosa, Solideal Nederland BV, Deutsche Hefewerke GmbH

Financial Controller for 4 different companies trading Kaolin (white clay used in paper industry): 
- Dutch agency company;
- Belgium production/trade company; 
- 2 Brazilian trade companies.

I was responsible for the Accounting Systems, Budgets, Management Reports, Statutory Accounts as well as VAT and Corporate Tax.
